item.title: A Little About Me
item.description: Hello Friends :) # Hello again, my name is Yohannes Molla, and I am a passionate coder and problem solver from Ethiopia. I discovered my love for coding at the young age of 15 and have been hooked ever since. As a high school graduate, I have dedicated my life to programming and finding innovative solutions to complex problems. I am a true coding enthusiast who loves to explore new technologies and programming languages.
